game.name: Jumpy Jax
game.description:
The biggest adventure journey is just about to begin today with our brand new jumping puzzle! Are you ready to be enrolled in it and crack all your previous records you have made before? Join Jumpy Jax game and prove the world that you are skilled enough to help any character to make perfect jumps! This cool character Jumpy Jax has only one that is to fly in the sky. However, many deadly obstacles would be there to stop him from making his dream come true. 
 
He believes on your jumping skill. So, join the fun to guide him to the victory in a sky that is full of death-defying challenges. Do not forget to grab the coins that you see during the gameplay. This path includes several obstacles that would keep moving from upward to downward or vice versa. In this cool html5 jumping game, your objective is to go as far as possible while avoiding the death. The coins you collect will help to raise your level. 

Your entry in the new level also comes with an extra life. Click the screen using your mouse when you are on your PC or tap the screen when you are on mobile phone! Do your best to set your best score in each level in this online kids game! When you finish the game, you can check how much distance you have covered, which level you have reached, and how much score you have created. Good luck to challenge your skill in our more endless runner games!
